gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Rockets 101, Jazz 100
gameRecap.excerpt: Houston defeats Utah, 101-100 as they win their 11th straight game and improve to 38-35. Jalen Green led Houston with 34 points, nine rebounds, six assists, and 4 3PM as Amen Thompson added 18 points and 14 rebounds. John Collins led Utah with a season-high 30 points, along with 11 rebounds while Collin Sexton added 29 points. The Jazz fall to 29-45.
